Great professor! Recommend him to anyone. No written homework, funny, and knows what he's talking about in lecture even though its boring sometimes.
 
 Has lots of practice tests to help you out, and review sessions before every test to go over all the problems on the practice test, TAKE ADVANTAGE! exam solutions and practice on website.
Not as good as Sonat Suer. He is grumpy, watch out! however, he is hilarious. He knows what he's talking about, he's really smart.
Very good math lecturer.  He is funny and knows how to teach calc.  He is a lot better than all the other Calc 230 professors who dont speak english.  No written HW due!
Best Calc 2 teacher. Really nice, jolly, and helpful/clear. Try and get him as your TA.
